balanceOfAt.t.sol
├── when user has no epochs
│   └── it should return 0
└── when user has epochs
    ├── when timestamp is before the first epoch
    │   └── it should return 0
    ├── when timestamp is within user's epoch range
    │   ├── when calculated bias is negative
    │   │   └── it should return 0
    │   └── when calculated bias is positive
    │       └── it should return the correct balance
    └── when timestamp is after the last epoch
        ├── when calculated bias is negative
        │   └── it should return 0
        └── when calculated bias is positive
            └── it should return the correct balance
